75
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,870
She's his girlfriend now.[br]I mean, what can we do?

76
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:02,590
There you go! That's the spirit[br]I' m looking for! "What can we do?"

77
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,920
