236
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:30,080
Okay. Okay, I'll go first.

237
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:32,320
So the other night. . .

238
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:35,840
. . .Rachel and I are in bed[br]talking about fantasies. . .

239
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:40,240
